[05:46.90]	[Descends]
[05:48.12]MACBETH	Then live, Macduff: what need I fear of thee?
[05:53.11]	But yet I'll make assurance double sure,
[05:57.80]	And take a bond of fate: thou shalt not live;
[06:02.89]	That I may tell pale-hearted fear it lies,
